{"ID":"20260609131321-cm4i5gm","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609131321-cm4i5gm","title":"2021年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609131334-xyiy60w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131334-xyiy60w","updated":"20260609131334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"新学期到来，我校推出一门全新的通识课“家常菜”，受到广大师生的关注和好评。过去，学校的劳动教育课程非常少，而且多是"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，很难培养学生的劳动意识和习惯。“家常菜”这门课找到了学生们感兴趣的切入点，学习难度不大，门槛不高，却能让学生"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131334-lgry7f3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131334-lgry7f3","updated":"20260609131334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（   ）。择菜，洗菜，切菜，准备配料并着手烹饪。通过"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，学生们不仅能够提升厨艺，还能真正体会到做菜的辛苦和乐趣，增加对食物的敬畏和感情，从而减少食物浪费，进一步养成"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的生活作风。期末考核时，学生的“作品”会摆在食堂的专门窗口，供师生们品鉴，这又会给学生带来满满的成就感。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131334-hfhatwf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131334-hfhatwf","updated":"20260609131334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"烧菜做饭作为一项生活技能，能让学生受益一生。更为重要的是，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"通过学习烧菜做饭还会增强学生对家务劳动的理解与认知，有助于在和家人的相处中更懂得体谅、更懂得感恩、更懂得分担"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131321-rrtxvau","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131321-rrtxvau","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-y8byy1b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-y8byy1b","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-ylclucq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-ylclucq","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．纸上谈兵    受益匪浅    自己动手    勤俭节约"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-uhk7140","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-uhk7140","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．形同虚设    受益匪浅    身体力行    吃苦耐劳"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-p2nl4oq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-p2nl4oq","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．形同虚设    不虚此行    自己动手    吃苦耐劳"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-lyqn2t5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-lyqn2t5","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．纸上谈兵    不虚此行    身体力行    勤俭节约"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-zdrz4e2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-zdrz4e2","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．下列填入文中括号内的语句，衔接最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-0gizj0z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-0gizj0z","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．劳动者在幕后辛勤付出，才做出了一道道家常菜"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-n2bwyng","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-n2bwyng","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．劳动者在幕后的辛勤付出，都承载于一道道家常菜"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-71t0eqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-71t0eqh","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．一道家常菜，通常承载着劳动者在幕后的辛勤付出"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-ytta84o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-ytta84o","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．一道家常菜，劳动者在幕后通常有着辛勤的付出"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-vxh30se","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-vxh30se","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画波浪线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-i1ydhag","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-i1ydhag","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．学习烧菜做饭还会增强学生对家务劳动的理解与认知，有助于在和家人的相处中更懂得体谅、更懂得感恩、更懂得分担。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-5x6m9ha","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-5x6m9ha","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．学习烧菜做饭还会增强学生对家务劳动的理解与认知，有助于他们在和家人的相处中更懂得体谅、更懂得感恩、更懂得分担。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-0g6gb8y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-0g6gb8y","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．通过学习烧菜做饭还会增强学生对家务劳动的理解与认知，有助于他们在和家人的相处中更懂得体谅、更懂得感恩、更懂得分担。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131348-n4azdwo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131348-n4azdwo","updated":"20260609131348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．通过学习烧菜做饭还会使学生对家务劳动的理解与认知得以增强，有助于在和家人的相处中更懂得体谅、更懂得感恩、更懂得分担。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131321-p3nxbq8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131321-p3nxbq8","updated":"20260609131356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609131321-jd32mbq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131321-jd32mbq","updated":"20260609131356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．A    18．C    19．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609131321-156t735","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131321-156t735","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-y0nb3sa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-y0nb3sa","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查学生理解并正确使用词语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-631tw35","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-631tw35","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纸上谈兵：指在纸面上谈论打仗。比喻空谈理论，不能解决实际问题。也比喻空谈不能成为现实。形同虚设：形式上虽有，却不起作用。此处指课程多流于书面理论而没有实际操作，故选“纸上谈兵”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-v1tev7j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-v1tev7j","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不虚此行：没有空跑这一趟。表示某种行动还是有所收获的。受益匪浅：指收获不小，有很大的收获。此处指学生能从课程中获得很大好处，不局限于“此行”，应选“受益匪浅”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-orv7gla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-orv7gla","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自己动手：指亲自动手劳作，能够让自己吃饱穿暖。身体力行：一般多用来表示努力实践，亲身体验。此处强调的是学生能够自己动手操作，选“自己动手”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-ehary5t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-ehary5t","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吃苦耐劳：能过困苦的生活，也经得起劳累。勤俭节约：形容工作勤劳，生活节俭。根据前文“减少食物浪费”可见，强调的是“节约”，故选“勤俭节约”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-foroky0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-foroky0","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-tf7sp9e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-tf7sp9e","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生语言表达连贯之语句复位的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-y29iyse","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-y29iyse","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据后文衔接的“择菜，洗菜，切菜，准备配料并着手烹饪”可见，这些程序繁琐而辛苦，故“辛苦”应该放在后句与之衔接，排除AB。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-xykxiid","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-xykxiid","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.中途易辙，“一道家常菜”后没有谓语，主语偷换成“劳动者”，排除"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-7m8j8ql","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-7m8j8ql","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-b4h6jzf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-b4h6jzf","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-27l3iue","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-27l3iue","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"画线句语句有二，均为成分残缺，一滥用介词“通过”导致句子缺少主语，应删去；排除CD。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-obtpjt0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-obtpjt0","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二是“在和家人的相处中更懂得”前缺少主语，应加上“他们”，排除A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131408-elm9bhu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131408-elm9bhu","updated":"20260609131408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}